Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是市民已经渐渐开始赞同狂徒的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:51.91,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(872,660)}lunatic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了明确谁才是真正的正义使者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设法恢复对英雄的信赖才是最重要的事项吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:16.36,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让我们相信英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有现役的英雄光临我们英雄学会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\pos(640,590)}英雄学会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有这闲工夫 还不如去追查狂徒的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:33.43,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,660)}lunatic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦..但是上头吩咐恢复信赖关系要摆在第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他那样能够恢复得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里碰上只能算你气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由在下来传授英雄的真髓是也~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咻~啊咻~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位也一起来做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻 咻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉..好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还再说这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉..好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？连你也这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啦 刚才不是还在“咻咻咻”的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是强打精神而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我根本没有指导学生的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直都只是在旁边看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排名也是最末席..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只是在旁边看而已..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我的blog也灾难连连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灾难？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你不适合当英雄”之类..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“快罢手吧你”之类 全是这种留言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 话说你还有在弄blog啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最糟蹋英雄的信赖的一定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性格这么消极？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 校长老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 巴纳比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你变成了一位多可靠的英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了在这里的学习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能这么说校长很欣慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊万 你的活跃我也有看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请不要叫我的本名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不好不好 现在应该叫你折纸旋风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们都变得好出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~萌虎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好您好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个不是毕业生的家伙瞎掺和进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里！原人气英雄的登场一定会让学生们高兴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 不用加“原”啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人人气英雄是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有英雄才能呈现的特别讲座要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对英雄来说最重要的就是赚取分数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被别人抢走前先下手为强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是业界中的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对英雄来说最重要的是保护市民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此就算破坏大厦都在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意什么赔偿金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对英雄最重要的是对企业的宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当镜头对准自己的时候 要把LOGO摆在最显眼的位置是也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目标又不是在旁边看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 能不能告诉我们救人的诀窍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 也来看我的..看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我看看你们的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我的能力是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..就这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的皮肤能拉这么长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..笑容很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我可以流很多汗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也看看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能成为英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙的笑容都合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成为英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说果然是太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都说你毕业之后百分百成为英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是吊车尾..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我又不像爱德华那样有英雄向的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦 一定有只有你才能办到的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我才能做到的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩一定要一起成为英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指导！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以他们的能力要做英雄应该够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是NEXT倒更像达人秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛虎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能来看看我的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 不用学我说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 不用学我说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 我说真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 我说真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我差不多一点啊 折纸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这能力好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连人都可以模仿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个没法用在救人上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 只要变成我使用百倍神力就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能复制外表 但不是连能力都能复制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我这能力不适合当英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人应该放弃当英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像变得我都伤心起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以别用那张脸唉声叹气？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要这么担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定存在只有折纸的能力才能做得到的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前被别人说过同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个朋友是学年第一的NEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那话出自他的嘴里让我没法当真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人没有成为英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却成为了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说折纸更适合当英雄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这回事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别谦虚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说不是了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才应该成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀~在学生时代的时候无论让你做什么都能出色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说你可是全校学生都仰慕的对象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你的粉丝俱乐部都成立了..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都和你戴着一样的眼镜..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别再说这种让人害臊的往事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问..到底是怎样的学生啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的..不要再问了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦..不是兔子 我问的是折纸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊万同学啊 是个很乖的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个很要好的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他一直躲在那孩子的背影里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就是学年第一NEXT的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是个非常优秀的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在在学期间惹出一个事件..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事对我校来说也是一段苦涩的回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我准备车子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上 伊万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们来解决这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是校则规定不能在外面使用能力..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量是为了救人而存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不用更待何时？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以我的能力..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我会支援你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是..没有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样没法当英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗 我真的要杀人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了这条心吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊 混小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊万 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 伊万！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事我也有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是事故 但是据说这里出了杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后爱德华锒铛入狱 同而失去了当英雄的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那家伙才..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才应该成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人现在也还在监狱里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像经常在这里听你倾诉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里？你不是还..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来复仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃狱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在数日之前来了通知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我的痛苦吗 啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还差一点就成为英雄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候你什么都没做？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么去救人的我是罪犯 而你却成了英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的关系我失去了一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折纸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样能让他消气的话 我被杀都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是我把他的人生搞的一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华对你泄恨是本末倒置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我所听到的来说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折纸学长并没有过错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那时候他期待我伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那时我有所行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就可以成为英雄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为一个比我还要出色的英雄..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错 是我..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才阻止你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你那家伙才背负了罪孽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想要让他的罪孽更加深重？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我什么都..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想重复那次的失败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊万 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 伊万！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是英雄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我的话可真经典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃..自己夸起自己来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样 丢人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你有一个好搭档呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在干这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爱德华！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪孽深重之人啊 时机已到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂徒..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.62,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,660)}lunatic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么找上我..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你犯下杀人之祸非但不求赎罪还进而逃狱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就以你的身体来偿还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚昧..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是英雄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为能逃得出我的手掌心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目标是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我干掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无益的杀生有违我的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有罪之人请向前一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我才是真的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你要偿还自己的罪孽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人全都阴险狡猾..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受正义的制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华由我来保护！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来保护！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 包庇罪人之人亦是罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休要逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 折纸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么盯上爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙和噬身之蛇应该没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了组织的灭口而行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了让恶人偿还罪孽而来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说你不是噬身之蛇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的搅局 导致噬身之蛇的线索都断了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来啊兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无谋之举..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被仇恨冲昏了头脑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聆听塔纳托斯的幽叹吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.87,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(570,660)}Thanatos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦..应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以冷静一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们英雄的争斗并非我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只向犯下杀生大祸的恶人索求同等的赔偿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就..杀人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那即是我的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的正义就是抓住像你这样的笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你口中之正义的下场..就由我亲眼来见证吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起重新开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的失败..还有爱德华的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能弄清那个手印脸不是噬身之蛇是件好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不好么..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的英雄亲善活动在各地如火如荼地展开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中我想特别赞扬折纸旋风的活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的在下..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将不仅仅只会一招见切之术是也！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咻！咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼..好痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说你不是噬身之蛇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我这么..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不想和你搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算借助你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:55.18,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,550)}{\fs52}{\fad(550,0)}#08
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:55.18,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1054,550)}{\fad(550,0)}机会一定会来
